Meet OBWS Founders Club founding member Tracy Green, Co-Founder & CEO of the luxury, vibrant, fashion-forward eyewear brand @VontelleEyewear! Each of their products are designed to pay homage to our African ancestry with traditional colors and patterns that channel our African, Caribbean, and Latin heritage. 🙌🏾⁠

'We hope to gain increased brand exposure and meet with other businesses needing advice on anything - entrepreneurship is tough and you need community.' - Tracy⁠
